{
  "stem": "3721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then, when we got to a city by the name Beregszasz, gendarmes came up and took us from-- off the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then somehow, the, the local police-- there were the gendarmes and the city police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The local police were a little more friendly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were telling us that they just-- the Americans bombed the, the train station in Kosice, in Kassa, and that they totally devastated it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were going to take us to, to Kassa to some concentration camp or relocation lager.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we can't go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Therefore, we're going to stay here for a day or two.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They can repair it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They'll take us there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "If not, they'll take us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were there about two, three days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they didn't feed us there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "No, they, they were not so friendly as the people in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I spoke to one of the local gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I told them that if you save us, then I will find some gold that was hidden by somebody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know where it is from here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I, I will find it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I'll reward you for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he said that he cannot do it all four of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But he'll try to do one or two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But anyway, this negotiation got nowhere, because then, once-- early in the morning, they took us, put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they shipped us to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And in Budapest, I was in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I don't know if you know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did you ever hear of the [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was a center of war criminals, where they brought you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they put you in jail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you were a, a non-Jew, they put you in jail.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
